. The forecast of the strong enough influence of\nantiferrodistortive order parameter on the transition temperatures and so on\nthe phase diagrams and properties of multiferroics is made on the basis of the\ndeveloped theory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 19 Jul 2015 21:13:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-17"}
