equire any dependency modeling between PDs and\nmacroeconomic variables, which often proves to be cumbersome and unstable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Jul 2015 08:36:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 28 Dec 2020 03:32:45 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 15 Jan 2022 11:41:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-19"}
